# Generated protobuf code (Pillar A4). The .proto sources under proto/
# are the source of truth; gen/ is reproduced from them by `make proto-gen`
# (or `buf generate`) and is regenerated by CI before every build/test
# step (see .github/workflows/ci.yml). Tracking generated code makes
# every proto change a +40k-line diff that overwhelms automated review
# tools and obscures the actual schema change. Contributors run
# `make proto-gen` once after a fresh clone; the Devin environment
# blueprint installs the buf toolchain so this is a one-time step.
gen/
